1.plot: Curious about the Marvel workout collection from Her Universe available NOW at Kohl's? Lindz and Scruffy talk sizing, designs, and pricing!!

2.title: Her Universe Fashion Show UPDATES!
2.plot: With the deadline to enter just a FEW WEEKS AWAY, we tell you some of the exciting NEW CHANGES for this year's show at San Diego Comic Con.

3.title: Her Universe Fashion Show, Open Call!
3.plot: We went to the Her Universe Fashion Show Open Call!

locations: Hollywood & Highland Center, Hollywood, Los Angeles, California, USA::(exterior scenes)
imdb.plot outline: While shirt and jeans are enjoyable and comfy to wear, they used to be the only way a girl could express her fandom through clothing. Those days are long past thanks to companies finally realizing that girls very much want to be fashionable AND geeky at the same time! There's a style for every geek, and we're here to help share and show you all the wonderful geek fashions that can be had.
